POD1000000005_S0000382	and with retail moving more and more online forever twenty-one's weak e-commerce game didn't help matters
POD1000000005_S0000383	in recent years there's been one other major issue tugging at forever twenty-one's flouncy hem sustainability cause sustainable it ain't
POD1000000005_S0000384	i wonder is fast fashion if we're talking about sustainability like is that just as bad as it can get
POD1000000005_S0000385	well i'm i'm hesitant to say the worst but i would be hard-pressed to think of another realm of the fashion industry that is as bad
POD1000000005_S0000386	because fast fashion has as its fundamental purpose
