POD1000000024_S0000192	i'm like paired up with an olympian and now we have to do hurdles
POD1000000024_S0000194	you know a lot of books that are co-written
POD1000000024_S0000195	you know in this fifty-fifty way have you know chapter one is by one person and then chapter two is by the other person and they kind of volley back and forth
POD1000000024_S0000196	and we made a choice pretty early on that we wanted to have one narrative
POD1000000024_S0000197	and so as a project it is really impossible to disentangle our various inputs
POD1000000024_S0000198	and i don't know i feel like that feels truer to me in the sense of like that's really what a friendship feels like
POD1000000024_S0000199	and the way we did that is we outline together quite meticulously and then we would take a section of the outline split up
POD1000000024_S0000200	we'd each write narratively that section of the outline on our separate computers and then we would each read aloud what we had written to the other
POD1000000024_S0000201	and then we would knit them together and keep the best parts of both and then move on to the next section of the outline for seventy thousand words
POD1000000024_S0000202	wow
POD1000000024_S0000203	can you believe we did that
POD1000000024_S0000204	i'm just like saying that out loud it's wild
POD1000000024_S0000206	my truly like favorite moments of our writing process is when i would be frustrated or ready to give up and i would look around
POD1000000024_S0000207	and you were typing away furiously with your signature ann friedman typing noises and exclaim out loud i love words those were the moments
POD1000000024_S0000208	i can't believe you're outing me like this
POD1000000024_S0000209	i am outing you you are a capricorn writer and it is disgusting to be a part of but also it's you know i'm like we got we did it
POD1000000024_S0000210	my favorite moments are hearing you from like the other end of the house be like okay okay
POD1000000024_S0000212	like i can tell you we're really working through something
POD1000000024_S0000213	like you had really had a breakthrough
POD1000000024_S0000215	one thing that is truly consistent across every year of our friendship is that like i always do want to know what you think
POD1000000024_S0000216	i always do think you have the best jokes
POD1000000024_S0000217	like that is like never ever changed
