YOU1000000021_S0000000	released by square enix in two thousand and seven on the playstation portable director hajime tabata and writer kazushige nojima worked together to create a prequel of final fantasy seven for it's tenth anniversary
YOU1000000021_S0000001	the game sets up the world and role of many characters from the main game and focuses on developing several figures such as zack aerith sephiroth and key members of shinra
YOU1000000021_S0000002	the story and game player done solely from the perspective of zack and features full voice acting for combat random encounters are utilized while actual combat is similar to the kingdom heart's menu based real time system
YOU1000000021_S0000003	mechanics such as the equipment and material system have the majorly over hauled and removed to reduce player micromanagement and instead contribute to the main battle modifier the digital mind wave
YOU1000000021_S0000004	the d m w is a continuously spinning slot machine system that confers various bonuses effects and attacks based on the results including how zack levels up
YOU1000000021_S0000005	the campaign is progressed through missions the player can select at their own pace or complete side quests instead traveling instantly to many fully three-d areas and dungeons with no need for an over world map
YOU1000000021_S0000006	the story only gets larger from here so it's cut it down to size with a recapitulation
YOU1000000021_S0000007	the game begins with zack fair soldier second class of the group called soldier a private military army owned by the shinra electric power company in the city of midgar
YOU1000000021_S0000008	he completes a training exercise under the mentorship of his friend and commander angeal a first class soldier
